  <li>OpenBSD works hard to maintain the
      <a href="../policy.html">license policy</a> and
      <a href="../security.html">security</a> of the project.
      For this reason, some newer versions of some software which fail to meet
      either the license or security goals of the project have not been
      integrated into OpenBSD.
