<li><b>libexpat is now part of <tt>base43.tgz</tt>, not part of
<tt>xbase43.tgz</tt> (as in 4.2), nor a package (4.1 and before)</b><br>
This should simplify life for many users.
More details in the <a href="upgrade43.html#libexpat">4.3 Upgrade
Guide</a>
d384 4
a387 3
<li><b>hoststated(8) is now named relayd(8).</b><br>
More details in the <a href="upgrade43.html#relayd">4.3 Upgrade
Guide</a>
d390 3
a392 4
<li><b>New SMP support:</b><br>
<a href="../sparc64.html">OpenBSD/sparc64</a> and
<a href="../mvme88k.html">OpenBSD/mvme88k</a> now support multiple
processors.
d395 5
