        environment.</li> 
    <li>OpenBSD benefits from strong on-going development in many areas, 
d146 3
a148 3
        international community of programmers and end-users.</li>
    <li>OpenBSD offers opportunities for ordinary people to participate in the 
        development and testing of the product.</li> 
